3301 Victory Boulevard, west side, south of Speedwell Avenue, showing the J. Vroome House (Butler's 1853 map). On subsequent maps, those of 1874 and 1898, it appears as the Vroom house. In 1907 and 1917 it was owned by D. B. Boscher (Boschen).

May 19, 1932

P. L. Sperr
